  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "In this project, we use unsupervised learning models to cluster unlabeled documents into different groups, visualize the results and identify their latent topics/structures."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Contents"
   ]
  },
